description:
Do you sometimes find yourself counting your blessings? Well, now's the time to start doing it audibly!
In this karaoke video, You can sing some of my favorite blessings songs in a lower key. Whether you're looking for a fun way to spend your weekend or a way to relax after a long day, karaoke is the perfect remedy! So come on, let's start counting our blessings together!

Music performed by C Lalhmuaka (Hmuaka), 3 Sisters  youtube channel!
